oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: J. Veltman's Plumbing and Machine Shop
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior view of J. Veltman's Plumbing and Machine Shop at 216 West Wood Street. Pictured are Rose Veltman, age 19, Mary Veltman age 5, Charles Veltman, age 17, J. Veltman, and Fred Bruhn. There are several machine belts throughout the shop.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Plumbing industry; Machinery
